136
00:12:23.566 --> 00:12:24.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
はあ…

137
00:12:24.933 --> 00:12:28.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ご両親と海外生活 すごいッスね

138
00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:32.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
