147
00:12:56.733 --> 00:12:58.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
マスター ラーメン

148
00:12:58.600 --> 00:12:59.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
