152
00:13:19.133 --> 00:13:20.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
猫舌なんで

153
00:13:32.266 --> 00:13:33.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
