154
00:13:33.833 --> 00:13:35.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いらっしゃい

155
00:13:36.033 --> 00:13:37.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
