156
00:13:40.166 --> 00:13:45.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
うちのラーメン食べたいって客の顔
拝みたくってさ

157
00:13:57.800 --> 00:13:58.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（ゲン）ビールでいいか？

158
00:14:08.766 --> 00:14:10.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そうだよな

159
00:14:11.166 --> 00:14:16.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
俺みてえな半端もんが相手じゃ
一緒に飲む気しねえよな

160
00:14:18.100 --> 00:14:23.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
兄貴分に てめえのケツ拭かせて
いい気なもんだな

161
00:14:25.500 --> 00:14:27.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
あんたなら
きっとそう言うと思ったよ

162
00:14:29.933 --> 00:14:34.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
俺が脅したって
顔色ひとつ変えなかったもんな

163
00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:40.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
やっちまったこと
なかったことにはできねえよ

164
00:14:43.166 --> 00:14:47.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
大事なのは
そのあと どうするかだ

165
00:14:52.866 --> 00:14:53.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
けど…

166
00:14:56.133 --> 00:14:58.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
俺 取り返しのつかねえこと…

167
00:14:59.200 --> 00:15:01.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）
取り返しがつかないってのは―

168
00:15:02.466 --> 00:15:06.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
何もしねえで嘆いてるやつの
言い訳じゃねえのか？

169
00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:22.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ありがとな

170
00:15:25.233 --> 00:15:26.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）おい

171
00:15:32.133 --> 00:15:34.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うちでラーメン食ってから行きなよ

172
00:15:36.100 --> 00:15:37.633  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
今日は ちゃんと―

173
00:15:39.566 --> 00:15:41.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
のり載っけてやるから

174
00:15:50.133 --> 00:15:51.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
前科は？

175
00:15:53.700 --> 00:15:54.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ねえよ

176
00:15:55.300 --> 00:15:57.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ないんですか？ ヤクザなのに

177
00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:58.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
悪(わり)いかよ

178
00:15:59.066 --> 00:16:00.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ちょっと切っただけでしょ？

179
00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:04.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
だったら傷害罪で
うまくいけば執行猶予つきますよ

180
00:16:05.166 --> 00:16:06.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
絶対(ぜってえ)だな

181
00:16:07.600 --> 00:16:08.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
多分… ねっ？

182
00:16:19.500 --> 00:16:22.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
父親に会わせてやりたかったな

183
00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:23.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（忠さん）ああ

184
00:16:24.900 --> 00:16:28.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
せっかく息子が
探しに来たっていうのによ

185
00:16:32.600 --> 00:16:33.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あっ…

186
00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:41.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おい

187
00:16:43.133 --> 00:16:43.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おい

188
00:16:45.600 --> 00:16:46.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
お前…

189
00:16:47.533 --> 00:16:48.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
健太なのか？

190
00:16:56.633 --> 00:16:57.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
どうも

191
00:16:58.500 --> 00:16:59.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
はじめまして

192
00:17:01.633 --> 00:17:04.599  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
何か食べたいのありますか？

193
00:17:05.733 --> 00:17:08.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うん？ うん… ラーメン

194
00:17:10.800 --> 00:17:13.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ここのインスタントですけど

195
00:17:15.933 --> 00:17:18.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
家(うち)じゃ食べらんないから

196
00:17:19.366 --> 00:17:23.099  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
インスタント好きじゃないんだ
お母さんが

197
00:17:25.800 --> 00:17:28.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
マスター ラーメン

198
00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:30.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）あいよ

199
00:18:21.766 --> 00:18:22.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うまい？

200
00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:27.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そっか

201
00:18:28.833 --> 00:18:30.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
また会えるよね？

202
00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:33.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おお

203
00:18:34.333 --> 00:18:37.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
今度 手紙書くから 住所どこ？

204
00:18:45.466 --> 00:18:48.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
今までどおり ここでいいんだよ

205
00:19:05.166 --> 00:19:06.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
元気でな

206
00:19:07.933 --> 00:19:09.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
お父さんもね

207
00:19:26.000 --> 00:19:27.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（ゲン）兄貴

208
00:19:30.633 --> 00:19:34.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
一人で大丈夫ッスから

209
00:19:35.300 --> 00:19:37.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
もう逃げませんから

210
00:19:39.166 --> 00:19:40.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
つきあわせろよ

211
00:19:49.200 --> 00:19:51.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
絶対 手紙書くからね

212
00:19:51.500 --> 00:19:53.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（忠さん）住所は ここだからな

213
00:20:11.266 --> 00:20:15.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
クリスマスってさ
幸せじゃなきゃいけなかったっけ

214
00:20:16.300 --> 00:20:19.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
さあ… 忘れちゃったわよ

215
00:20:20.666 --> 00:20:24.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
しかし 一年に一度きりなのに
僕も含めてですけど―

216
00:20:24.700 --> 00:20:27.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
こんな吹きだまりに集まるのは
どうなんでしょうか

217
00:20:30.766 --> 00:20:33.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
すいませんでした フフッ

218
00:20:36.566 --> 00:20:38.433  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（小寿々）あら 竜ちゃん

219
00:20:38.533 --> 00:20:40.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）よっ いらっしゃい

220
00:20:41.633 --> 00:20:43.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
執行猶予ついたよ

221
00:20:43.800 --> 00:20:46.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）へえ そう

222
00:20:47.333 --> 00:20:51.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
いろいろ みんなに
世話かけちまったから

223
00:20:55.166 --> 00:20:57.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（一同）ああっ！

224
00:20:58.766 --> 00:20:59.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（金本）カニ

225
00:20:59.633 --> 00:21:01.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（小寿々）カニ～ カニ

226
00:21:01.266 --> 00:21:04.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
サンタってホントにいるんだね
マスター

227
00:21:04.633 --> 00:21:08.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（ミキ･ルミ･カナ）
ねえ 早く食べようよ ねえねえ

228
00:21:08.366 --> 00:21:12.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）ようし じゃ今夜は
豪快に焼きガニといきましょう

229
00:21:13.000 --> 00:21:14.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（一同）わあっ！

230
00:21:56.500 --> 00:22:00.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）
これが本当のサイレントナイトさ

231
00:22:22.200 --> 00:22:23.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
行くのかい？

232
00:22:26.033 --> 00:22:28.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
居心地のいいところに
長居してると―

233
00:22:28.766 --> 00:22:30.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
そうじゃないとこに
行きたくなるんで

234
00:22:31.733 --> 00:22:33.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
やっかいな性分だな

235
00:22:35.066 --> 00:22:36.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
自分でも持て余してます

236
00:22:38.200 --> 00:22:40.033  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
それとこれ

237
00:22:40.500 --> 00:22:42.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
今までツケにしてもらった分です

238
00:22:43.200 --> 00:22:44.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
しまいなよ

239
00:22:45.233 --> 00:22:49.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
新しい土地に行けば
何かと物入りだ

240
00:22:50.033 --> 00:22:51.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
受け取ってください

241
00:22:52.300 --> 00:22:55.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
今度の旅は
少し長くなりそうなんで

242
00:22:56.600 --> 00:22:57.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
そうかい

243
00:23:05.766 --> 00:23:06.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
じゃ

244
00:23:13.666 --> 00:23:16.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
その傷の落とし前
必ずつけますから

245
00:23:17.833 --> 00:23:19.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）世の中は―

246
00:23:21.833 --> 00:23:25.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
さすらい迷って 戻り川

247
00:23:30.266 --> 00:23:32.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
人生なめんなよ

248
00:24:20.433 --> 00:24:21.633  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いらっしゃい

249
00:24:23.866 --> 00:24:26.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
メニューになくても
できるもんなら―

250
00:24:27.766 --> 00:24:29.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
何でも作るよ

251
00:24:35.900 --> 00:24:40.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
♪～

